Kafka commands
Start Kafka Server - 
~/kafka_2.13-3.7.0/bin/kafka-server-start.sh ~/kafka_2.13-3.7.0/config/kraft/server.properties

Create Topic - 
kafka-topics.sh --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --topic airfoil --create --partitions 1 --replication-factor 1

List All Topics - 
kafka-topics.sh --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --list
